# Navigation and Routing Standards

## Route Structure
```typescript
const routes = {
  home: '/',
  player: {
    profile: '/player/:steamId',
    search: '/players/search',
  },
  builds: {
    list: '/builds',
    create: '/builds/create',
    view: '/builds/:id',
    edit: '/builds/:id/edit',
  },
  auth: {
    steam: '/auth/steam',
    callback: '/auth/steam/callback',
  },
  analytics: '/analytics',
  premium: '/premium',
}
```

## Navigation Components
- Header/Navbar:
  ```tsx
  <header class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm sticky top-0 z-40">
    <nav class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <Logo />
